# Import Text fixtures consumed byte-for-byte by the `import_text_*` tests
# (crates/nub-cli/tests/integration.rs). The tests assert the raw file text,
# including its `\n` line endings. Windows runners default to autocrlf=true,
# which would rewrite these to CRLF on checkout and break the string match.
tests/fixtures/import-text/* text eol=lf
tests/fixtures/import-text-named/* text eol=lf
